  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/ac7445eaf52ac6e3c00e85df62355faa.poster.avif?t=1774237936\" width=1170 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/ac7445eaf52ac6e3c00e85df62355faa.webm?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/ac7445eaf52ac6e3c00e85df62355faa.mp4?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the peaceful town of Aurora, a quiet place where you can build the life you’ve always dreamed of. Grow your farm, make new friends, and take part in the flow of the seasons. Help restore the Aurora town to its former glory and bring peace back to the land! <br> <br>What do you can experience in this game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Build and expand</strong> your farm with crops, animals, and decorations. <br>💞 <strong>Connect with the townsfolk</strong> through meaningful relationships.<br>🎣 <strong>Enjoy relaxing activities</strong> like fishing, mining, cooking, and crafting. <br>🎉 <strong>Celebrate festivals</strong>, take on part-time jobs, and help shape Aurora’s future. <br>🌿<strong> Reveal the secrets behind Aurora town.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/704af694b0a716bc844b4407eb770b9a.poster.avif?t=1774237936\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/704af694b0a716bc844b4407eb770b9a.webm?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/704af694b0a716bc844b4407eb770b9a.mp4?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/ac7445eaf52ac6e3c00e85df62355faa.poster.avif?t=1774237936\" width=1170 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/ac7445eaf52ac6e3c00e85df62355faa.webm?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/ac7445eaf52ac6e3c00e85df62355faa.mp4?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the peaceful town of Aurora, a quiet place where you can build the life you’ve always dreamed of. Grow your farm, make new friends, and take part in the flow of the seasons. Help restore the Aurora town to its former glory and bring peace back to the land! <br> <br>What do you can experience in this game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Build and expand</strong> your farm with crops, animals, and decorations. <br>💞 <strong>Connect with the townsfolk</strong> through meaningful relationships.<br>🎣 <strong>Enjoy relaxing activities</strong> like fishing, mining, cooking, and crafting. <br>🎉 <strong>Celebrate festivals</strong>, take on part-time jobs, and help shape Aurora’s future. <br>🌿<strong> Reveal the secrets behind Aurora town.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/704af694b0a716bc844b4407eb770b9a.poster.avif?t=1774237936\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/704af694b0a716bc844b4407eb770b9a.webm?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156360/extras/704af694b0a716bc844b4407eb770b9a.mp4?t=1774237936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
